KKran
================================================

Version: 1.1.0
Date: 2025-12-23
Author: Kosei Kawaguchi a.k.a. KKTeX
License: MIT
Link: https://github.com/KKTeX/KKran
Support: p.c.aces1056@gmail.com

Description:
------------
This is a package that offers commands for generating answer fields used in tests and exams. It is compatible with both vertical and horizontal text formatting.
The package name originates from "æ¬„ (:ran)", which means a small piece of area.

Dependencies:
-------------
calc, tikz, xcolor, KKsymbols, kvoptions, luacode

Notice
-------------
This package is **LuaLaTeX-only**. 

See kkran-doc.tex for usage examples.